            | ARTP2 (Adaptive Rank Truncated Product - Version 2) is an R package of biological pathway association analysis or pathway meta-analysis for genome-wide association studies (GWAS). 
            | It also provides tools for gene-level association test as a special case. ARTP2 is an enhanced version of two previously released packages ARTP and AdaJoint.
        p
            span 
