                | when only SNP-level summary statistics from one or multiple GWAS were available. We provide reference panel data incorporated from the 
            a(href="http://www.1000genomes.org/") 1000 Genomes Project
            span  to facilitate the studies on various populations. We also support over 4,700 pathways predefined by the 
